    "installation": "从CRAN安装: install.packages(\"biomartr\"); 开发版安装: BiocManager::install(\"ropensci/biomartr\"); Bioconda安装: conda install r-biomartr",
    "basic_usage": "使用getCollection()函数检索基因组及相关数据文件",
    "examples": [
      "getCollection(organism = \"Homo sapiens\", type = \"genome\", database = \"ensembl\")",
      "getCollection(organism = \"Mus musculus\", type = \"proteome\", database = \"refseq\")"
